  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      1. Intravitreal injection can induce perioperative stress for the patients.

        2. Different factors can modulate the pre-operative fear and physiologic reaction.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to assess the influence of perioperative factors on objective outcome
      measures, which indicate the physiologic stress reaction.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
